{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require glasses used in licenced establishments to be marked with the crown",
        "additional_details": "As Government service and tourism industry need all the help, require the crown be used on glasses in licensed establishments. This would help reassure citizens and tourists their drink is the correct measurement.",
        "background": "Now we no longer need CE on glasses in licensed establishments, the Government should require the crown mark be used once more.\r\n \r\nI have seen new markings on pub glasses, but surely the crown mark should return.",
